page.html:
I don't know exactly what to say here.. Hi.


Zootopia Duo





A fair goodbye to an amazing person

SleepyDarkrai
SleepyDarkrai was someone that I honestly didn't know at all joining the Osu Mania community, in fact, it was only recently that i actually had started talking to him. Thank god Yip gave me the invite to the server he was in.
We started off on the wrong foot. I said stupid shit how i found Apparition easy while i could only A it. Right on new years eve this was, i remember it vividly, but this isn't a bad memory, it's just him being him, and I actually look back on it and appreciate it more and more because I actually realised how stupid I sounded.
I wearily joined a voice call he was in a few weeks later or so, I can't be exact when it was, and we talked like we had never had the argument, it surprised me at first, but I wasn't about to pass up a chance to talk to him normally after what had happened.
I then received a message from him, I think a day or two later, and to my surprise he had apologised. It took me by shock at first, I thought he was just calling me out for being an idiot, but he was sincere, and since the voice call had found me quite nice. I was quite happy to be honest, I hated having annoyed him enough for him to call me out.

And that's where it all began

Supportive, Humorous, an overall enjoyable person to be around, I always found laughter wherever he was, and I admired it.
I had someone who was far ahead of me, but still within reach if i tried, and I always found myself over competing to beat his scores, which of course would never happen because he was quite a lot better

Except for blastix gravity, love you bb but i can mash for days

Darkrai. As i said before, not a day on this game will go by with me not missing you, it'll feel like a gap is gone from this game for me, a gap belonging to you, because you really did make an impact on both my skill and me as a person.

You are so amazing, stay strong and stay banterous.

- Dom xx
